Magic Story:
Immortal Sun disappears, and Angrath angrily leave. St. Elenda arrives and explains her role as a vampire, as a guardian of the sun. After Vona interjects, she forces them to take her to Queen Miralda.
Huatli and Tishana opt to lead their people to share Orazca.
Huatli returns to the capital to speak to the Emperor. To the shock of no one, the Emperor has his mind set on Conquest.
Huatli is encouraged to record stories of other planes, as her title is meant to, by her family and she leaves Ixalan.
Fun note, Huatli arrives at the capital by riding Zacama.
